---
import Page from "../layouts/Page.astro";
---

<Page title="Publications" description="My published works">
  <div class="prose prose-sm sm:prose-base lg:prose-lg max-w-none">
    <header class="mb-6 lg:mb-8">
      <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl text-jlp-burnt">Publications</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="space-y-8 lg:space-y-10">
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl text-jlp-burnt mb-4">Anthology Publications</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-3 lg:space-y-4">
          <li class="text-sm sm:text-base">
            <a href="http://www.amazon.com/Dusted-An-Anthology-Short-Stories/dp/1617060305/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&qid=1332718193&sr=8-1" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="font-semibold hover:text-jlp-burnt transition-colors">Suttee</a> was published in the Dusted anthology.
          </li>
          <li class="text-sm sm:text-base">
            <a href="http://neosalexandria.org/bibliotheca-alexandrina/current-titles/the-shining-cities-an-anthology-of-pagan-science-fiction/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="font-semibold hover:text-jlp-burnt transition-colors">The Dumb Supper</a> was published in The Shining Cities: An Anthology of Pagan Science Fiction.
          </li>
          <li class="text-sm sm:text-base">
            <a href="http://issuu.com/eclecticflash/docs/ef_september_2011?mode=window&backgroundColor=%23222222" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="font-semibold hover:text-jlp-burnt transition-colors">A King of Infinite Space</a> on Eclectic Flash.
          </li>
          <li class="text-sm sm:text-base">
            <span class="font-semibold">The Latest Model</span> on 365tomorrows.com. You can read the story on their site <a href="http://365tomorrows.com/11/10/the-latest-model/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:text-jlp-burnt transition-colors">here</a>, though a redesign has messed up the formatting.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl text-jlp-burnt mb-4">Stories from "<a href="http://jenniferlynparsons.com/book/the-man-who-walked/" class="hover:text-jlp-burnt transition-colors">The Man Who Walked</a>"</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-3 lg:space-y-4">
          <li class="text-sm sm:text-base">
            <a href="http://eternalhauntedsummer.com/issues/autumn-equinox-2013/anna-and-the-false-god/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="font-semibold hover:text-jlp-burnt transition-colors">Anna and the False God</a> on Eternal Haunted Summer.
          </li>
          <li class="text-sm sm:text-base">
            <a href="http://eternalhauntedsummer.com/issues/winter-solstice-2010/frogging/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="font-semibold hover:text-jlp-burnt transition-colors">Frogging</a> on Eternal Haunted Summer.
          </li>
          <li class="text-sm sm:text-base">
            <span class="font-semibold">Black as Hell and Bold as Brass</span> on Dark Valentine Magazine. Sadly, DV has cease publication and taken their site down.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl text-jlp-burnt mb-4">Stories on Luna Station Quarterly</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-3 lg:space-y-4">
          <li class="text-sm sm:text-base">
            <a href="https://www.lunastationquarterly.com/issues/036/" class="font-semibold hover:text-jlp-burnt transition-colors">Joinery</a>
          </li>
          <li class="text-sm sm:text-base">
            <a href="https://www.lunastationquarterly.com/issues/044/" class="font-semibold hover:text-jlp-burnt transition-colors">Silks</a>
          </li>
          <li class="text-sm sm:text-base">
            <a href="https://www.lunastationquarterly.com/issues/048/" class="font-semibold hover:text-jlp-burnt transition-colors">Blessing</a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</Page>
